tos_content:
Hamaaree sait ke niyam aur sharten graahakon ke lie ek maargadarshika ke roop mein kaam karatee hain, taaki unhen dikhaaya ja sake ki ve hamaaree sait ka upayog kaise karen aur isakee sevaon ka upayog kaise karen.


#pahala: probot sait ke lie saamaany sharten: -
1- is prshth par ullikhit sabhee niyam aur sharten sait ke sabhee upayogakartaon par laagoo hotee hain.
2 - ek baar jab graahak hamaaree sait par panjeekrt ho jaata hai, to isaka matalab hai ki vah is prshth mein varnit niyamon aur sharton aur bhavishy mein jode ja sakane vaale kisee bhee niyam se pooree tarah sahamat hai.
3 - sabhee graahakon ko yah pramaanit karana chaahie ki jo vyaktigat deta ve hamen pradaan karate hain vah sahee hai taaki ve sait par panjeekaran kar saken aur apanee sevaen praapt kar saken.
4 - ham sabhee graahakon kee poochhataachh ka svaagat karate hain, aur hamaare takaneekee sahaayata karmachaaree din bhar mein graahakon kee sabhee poochhataachh ka javaab dene ke lie taiyaar hain.
5 - hamaare lie kisee bhee samay niyam aur sharton ko badalana ya nae logon ko jodana sambhav hai, isalie ham krpaya graahakon ko samay-samay par unhen dekhane ke lie kahenge jo kisee nae niyam ke baare mein jaanate hain.


# sekand: probot vebasait ke upayog kee sharten: -
1. graahakon ko hamen sabhee aavashyak jaanakaaree aur deta pradaan karana chaahie aur yah 100% sahee hona chaahie.
2. hamaaree sait ke durupayog ya hamaaree sait kee achaanak viphalata ke parinaamasvaroop klaint ko huee kisee bhee kshati ke lie sait jimmedaar nahin hai.
3. any logon ko sadasyata bechane kee manaahee hai. keval graahak ko bots ka upayog karane ka adhikaar hai.
4. anadhikrt vyaavasaayik upayog mein hamaaree sevaon ka upayog karana nishiddh hai.
5- upayogakarta yah vishvaas dilaata hai ki usake bot ka upayog hamaaree sait ko nukasaan nahin pahunchaega aur hamaaree sait ke niyamon aur sharton ka ullanghan nahin karega.
6- upayogakarta yah vishvaas dilaata hai ki vah usase jaaree kisee bhee ullanghan ke lie jimmedaar hai, aur vah is ullanghan ke lie jimmedaar hai.
7- hamaaree sait ka prashaasan klaint ko hamaaree sait ke durupayog ke parinaamasvaroop kisee bhee nukasaan ya nukasaan kee jimmedaaree deta hai.
8- hamaare prashaasan ko yah adhikaar hai ki yadi vah hamaaree sait ke niyamon aur sharton ka ullanghan karata hai to kisee sadasy kee sadasyata ya khaata band kar sakata hai.

9- sait ke baahar deel karane kee manaahee hai, aur sait par kisee bhee tarah ka len-den karana chaahie taaki graahakon ke saath kisee tarah kee dhokhaadhadee aur dhokhaadhadee na ho.
10- kaanoon ke khilaaph hamaaree sevaon ka upayog karane ya hamaaree sait ya kisee any vyakti ko nukasaan pahunchaane ke lie mana kiya gaya hai.

# yah probot kee sait par maujood sevaon ya saamagree ka upayog ya pun: upayog, kopee ya pest karane ke lie mana kiya gaya hai, aur probot kee sait par maujood sab kuchh akele sait ke svaamitv mein hai, aur koee bhee vyakti in sharton ka ullanghan karata hai, vah khud ko ujaagar karega ya usakee kampanee ya usakee sait ya sait ke prashaasan dvaara daayitv aur abhiyojan ke lie usaka aavedan.
pp_content:
Ham apane priy graahakon ko hamaaree gopaneeyata neeti prshth padhane ke lie dhanyavaad dete hain. ham apane graahakon ko aashvast karate hain ki unaka vyaktigat deta aur jaanakaaree hamaaree sait par pooree tarah se surakshit hogee, kyonki ham in deta ko banae rakhane ke lie jimmedaar hain aur ham ise sanrakshit karane ke lie har tarah kee talaash karate hain. hamaare gopaneeyata neeti prshth mein kuchh aaitam shaamil hain:

1- deta aur jaanakaaree jo ham apane graahakon se anurodh karate hain:

probot sait graahakon se kuchh deta aur jaanakaaree ka anurodh karatee hai taaki hamaaree sait par panjeekaran kar saken aur apanee sevaon ka upayog kar saken, udaaharan ke lie hamaaree sait klaint ke ee-mel, usake naam aur phon nambar ka anurodh karatee hai aur use hamaare khaate par apane khaate ka paasavard banaana chaahie. hamaaree sait dvaara sait aur any jaanakaaree ka anurodh kiya ja sakata hai.

2- hamaaree sait par graahak kee jimmedaaree:

graahak hamaaree sait par apane khaate kee suraksha ke lie jimmedaar hai. use kisee ko apane khaate ke baare mein sanvedanasheel jaanakaaree nahin denee chaahie jaise ki kisee ko usake khaate ka paasavard dena, jisase graahak khaate ko kuchh nukasaan ho. hamaaree salaah hai ki hamaare graahak any logon ko koee nijee jaanakaaree na den.

3- ham apanee sait mein apane graahakon ke deta kee suraksha kaise karate hain: -

hamaaree sait hamaare graahakon ke vyaktigat deta aur soochana kee suraksha ke lie vishv star par sarvottam prakriyaon ka anusaran karatee hai. hamaaree sait sabhee graahakon ko sunishchit karatee hai ki unaka deta hamaare paas surakshit rahega. hamaaree sait klaint deta (gdpr) kee suraksha ke lie yooropeey sangh kee aavashyakataon ka anupaalan karatee hai.

: - 4- hamaaree sait mein klaint ke vitteey adhikaar

hamaaree sait prashaasan graahakon ke vitteey adhikaaron ke lie utsuk hai. shesh keval graahak ko aadesh prshth mein dikhaee dega. hamaaree sait graahakon ke vitteey deta ke saath kisee ko bhee pradaan nahin karegee

5- graahakon ke deta ke lie hamaaree sait ka upayog: -

hamaaree sait klaint deta ka upayog keval unhen apanee sevaen pradaan karane ke lie karatee hai, jab ham sait par upayogee jaanakaaree praapt karate hain aur usakee sevaon ka vikaas karate hain. jab ham graahak poochhataachh ka javaab dete hain, aur jab ham khareedaaree karate hain.

6. ham apane graahak deta kee suraksha ke lie yooropeey sangh kee aavashyakataon ka paalan karate hain:

yooropeey sangh ne ek kaanoon banaaya hai jo klaint deta kee suraksha karane mein bahut madad karata hai. ham klaint deta ko sanrakshit karane ke lie sabhee tareekon se kaam karate hain. yah kaanoon sabhee graahakon ko unake deta ko hataane ya sanshodhit karane kee anumati deta hai jab yah is deta ka ullanghan hota hai, aur hamaaree sait ko is ghatana kee soochana usake ghatana ke 72 ghanton ke bheetar denee chaahie.

7- hamaaree sait ke adhikaar: -

hamaaree sait ko apanee gopaneeyata neeti prshth ke kisee bhee aaitam ko sanshodhit karane ya kisee bhee samay isamen kuchh nae aaitam jodane ka poorn adhikaar hai yadi hamaare vyavasthaapak yah dekhate hain ki aisa karana aavashyak hai, isalie hamaare priy graahakon, aapako samay se ek nazar rakhana chaahie hamaaree gopaneeyata neeti prshth par samay hamaaree gopaneeyata neeti prshth par kie gae kisee bhee parivartan se avagat hone ke lie.

8. hamaaree sait ka kopeerait: -

probot sait se sambandhit kisee bhee cheez ko kopee ya pest, upayog ya pun: upayog karane kee sakht manaahee hai, is sait mein maujood koee bhee saamagree keval probot sait se sambandhit hai. koee bhee vyakti kisee probot sait kee kisee bhee saamagree ya sevaon kee kopee, pest ya upayog karata hai; vah sait ke prashaasan dvaara daayitv ya abhiyojan ke lie khud ko ya apanee sait ya apanee kampanee ko ujaagar karega.
rp_content:
ham sabhee graahakon ko gaarantee dete hain ki pratisthaapan aur dhanavaapasee prakriya hamaare saath aasaanee se kee jaegee; ham apane sabhee priy graahakon ko santusht karane ke lie kadee mehanat karate hain. graahak ek pratisthaapan seva ka anurodh kar sakate hain ya ek shart ke saath khareed kee taareekh ke 7 dinon ke bheetar vaapasee kar sakate hain:
1- pratisthaapan aur dhanavaapasee prakriya keval us vyakti ko le ja sakatee hai jisane hamase sevaen khareedee theen.
2- ordar nambar aur inavait ko spasht karake khareed kee pushti kee jaanee chaahie.
3- jab graahak pratisthaapan ka anurodh karata hai, to usane khareede gae bot ka upayog nahin kiya hoga.
